snippet.title: Lost Skies Gameplay Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2024
snippet.description:
Bossa Studios provided a first look at gameplay from Lost Skies, the sky-faring co-operative survival game where you set up shop on a series of floating islands. It's soaring onto PC soon. 

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#Lostskies #FutureGamesShow #FGS #futuregamesshow2024 #gamescom
